{"_path":"/maps/_product/user-research/user-research","_dir":"user-research","_draft":false,"_partial":true,"_locale":"","title":"用户研究","description":"用户研究方法、工具和实践","body":{"type":"root","children":[{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"主题"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"主题"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"/maps/_product/user-research/dovetail"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Dovetail"}]},{"type":"text","value":" - 定性研究平台"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"概述"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"概述"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"用户研究是产品设计和开发过程中的关键环节，通过系统化的方法收集、分析用户数据，以指导产品决策。用户研究方法包括定性研究（如访谈、可用性测试）和定量研究（如问卷调查、数据分析），帮助产品团队深入理解用户需求、行为模式和痛点，从而设计出更符合用户期望的产品。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"用户研究工具则帮助团队高效管理研究流程，从访谈记录、转录分析到洞察沉淀，形成可追溯的证据链，支撑产品假设验证和决策制定。"}]}],"toc":{"title":"","searchDepth":2,"depth":2,"links":[{"id":"主题","depth":2,"text":"主题"},{"id":"概述","depth":2,"text":"概述"}]}},"_type":"markdown","_id":"content:6.maps:_product:user-research:user-research.md","_source":"content","_file":"6.maps/_product/user-research/user-research.md","_stem":"6.maps/_product/user-research/user-research","_extension":"md"}